<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>Course Martini</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
		integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<%= csrf_meta_tags %>
	<%= csp_meta_tag %>

	<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
	<%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
	<style>
		.container-fluid {
			padding: 0;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="gradient">
			<div class="page-header" style="text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="color:white">Course Martini</h1>
				<h2 style="color:white">Enjoy a cup of Course Martini, shaken, not stirred.</h2>
				<br>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-lg-2 offset-lg-5">
						<div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
							<a class="btn btn-outline-light rounded-pill  btn-block"
								href="/homepage/home">Overview</a><br><br>
							<a class="btn btn-outline-light rounded-pill  btn-block" href="#about-us">About
								Us</a><br><br>
							<a class="btn btn-outline-light rounded-pill  btn-block" href="#get-started">Get Started</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="about">
			<div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
				<br><br>
					<h1 id="about-us">About Us</h1>
					<p>Course selection is a stage in universities where students have to decide their own path of
						reaching academic goals. Sometimes it is difficult to choose the course that best suits
						studentsâ€™ academic demands.<br><br>
						Course Martini, is a platform for students to share their own experiences
						on different courses CUHK provides. The reviews provided will guide others on course selecting
						decisions to
						improve the overall quality of their academic experience during the studying period.</p>	
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="arrow"  onclick="location.href ='#quote'" style="cursor: pointer;">
						<%= image_tag("arrow.png", size:"50x50", :alt => "arrow") %>
					</div>	
		<p>1</p>
		<div class="comment">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-10 offset-lg-1">
					<div class="quote" id="quote">
						<blockquote>
							&ldquo; When I was a freshman, course selection gave me a really hard time, because I do not
							know which
							course to choose, and which professor's style fits me more. Now, with Course Martini, making
							decisions
							on course selecting is just so much more easier! &rdquo;
							<cite>&mdash; Yuren Qin, Yr2</cite>
						</blockquote>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

			<div class="get-started gradient-light" >
				<h1 id ="get-started"> Get Started here!</h1>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">

						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-lg-4">
								<div class="card-btn">
									<div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm" onclick="location.href ='';"
										style="cursor: pointer;">
										<div class="card-img-top"
											style="background-color:#FFB6C1; width:100%; height:225px">
											<h2>Join us</h2>
										</div>
										<div class="card-body">
											<p class="card-text">
												Please join our community of Course Martini to share your opinions on
												courses, and
												improve the plateform.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="col-lg-4">
								<div class="card-btn">
									<div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm" onclick="location.href ='/search';"
										style="cursor: pointer;">
										<div class="card-img-top" style="background-color:#fc8cb4; height:225px">
											<h2>Trends!</h2>
										</div>
										<div class="card-body">
											<p class="card-text">Our platform have various type of graphs on course
												statstics based on the
												reviews collected.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="col-lg-4">
								<div class="card-btn">
									<div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm" onclick="location.href ='/users/sign_up';"
										style="cursor: pointer;">
										<div class="card-img-top" style="background-color:#fc749c; height:225px">
											<h2>Search</h2>
										</div>
										<div class="card-body">
											<p class="card-text">If you want to get started with our system directly,
												you may as well start your search first.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2" style="text-align: center;">
								<h2>Already a member?</h2>
								<a type="button" href="/users/sign_in" class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-warning">Sign in here!</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		<div class="end">
			<p>Created by team Course Martini</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"
		integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n"
		crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
		integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
		crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
		integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6"
		crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>
